Better Reddit Check - a Chrome extension

Receive instant visual feedback whether any URL has been submitted to Reddit.
If the page you're on has been submitted, you can open a new tab to join the
discussion, or you can resubmit the link. Otherwise, you can start a new
submission right from the Chrome toolbar.

Better Reddit Check is based on the Reddit Check extension by Hrishikesh
Bakshi. It is maintained by paulburton0 [at] gmail.com

Better Reddit Check is distributed under the GNU General Public License - see
the accompanying LICENSE file for more details.
 
Extension install link:
https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/bnikifloagjncfjbniboapgdehnlemmd

Source available at:
